    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Rooms, buildings, or groups of buildings where the aerodynamic properties of something are studied, as how the shape of an object may affect the flow of air and other gases in motion around and through it.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
